translate chinese b1c04ss06_8b5ded49:

    # mc "Her method of parenting revolved around encouragement and growth, without punishment."
    mc "她的教育方法围绕着鼓励和成长，没有惩罚。"

# game/code/Book-1/Chapter-4s/s06.rpy:77
translate chinese b1c04ss06_15ca8c29:

    # mc "I guess that method worked a lot better for me. She communicated and connected with me a lot better, and I enjoyed that."
    mc "我想这种方法对我来说更有效。她和我的沟通和联系更好更亲密，我很喜欢这样。"

# game/code/Book-1/Chapter-4s/s06.rpy:80
translate chinese b1c04ss06_7bad173e:

    # sm "I got along better with my mom, too. Well, my foster mom, anyway."
    sm "我和妈妈也相处得更好。不过，是我的养母。"

# game/code/Book-1/Chapter-4s/s06.rpy:83
